      <notesStmt>
        <note>Title from colophon. Listed in New Cat. Cat. as Gāyatrīhṛdaya(-Upaniṣad).</note>
        <note>Text in the form of a dialogue between Svayaṁbhū (Brahmā) and Yājñavalkya.</note>
        <note>Written 8-10 lines per leaf.</note>
        <note>Good condition. Mistakes crossed through, covered over with yellow, or blocked out or blotched out with black. Marginal and interlinear corrections and one marginal insertion.</note>
        <note>Begins (f. 1v): śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ namaskṛtya bhagavān yājñavalkya svayaṁbhuvaṁ paripṛchati tan no brūhi bhagavān gāyatryutpatiṁ turiyaṁ śrotum ichāmi brahmajñānotpatiṁ prakṛtiṁ parīpṛchāmi śrībhagavān uvāca</note>
        <note>Ends (f. 11v): ya idaṁ nityam adhīyāno brāhmaṇāḥ prātaḥ śuciḥ sarvai pāpai pramucyate brahmaloke mahiyate</note>
        <note>Colophon (f. 11v): ity āha bhagavān yājñavalkyaḥ gāyatrīhṛdayaṁ sampūrṇaṁ</note>
      </notesStmt>
